@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_zxgjey(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.cos((v2 + 0.83 - v1 + 0.40)) - ((v2 + 0.32 + v2 + 0.67) * tmp))
    v2 = (wp.sin((v0 + 0.23 - v1 + 0.91)) - wp.sin((v0 + 0.37 * v1 + 0.37)))
    v0 = (0.22 * (wp.cos(v2 + 0.01) * wp.exp(tmp + 0.34)))
    data[tid] = v0
